Supermarket Sales Data Preprocessing and Visualization

________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

Objective

The objective of this assignment is to learn how to clean, preprocess, analyze, and visualize real-world data using Pandas and Matplotlib. Students will apply various data preprocessing techniques and create meaningful visualizations to gain business insights from a supermarket sales dataset.

________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

Dataset

Download the dataset from Kaggle:

Supermarket Sales Dataset

https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/aungpyaeap/supermarket-sales

________________________________________________________________________________________________________________


Dataset Columns

The dataset contains the following columns:

Invoice ID
Branch
City
Customer Type
Gender
Product Line
Unit Price
Quantity
Tax 5%
Total
Date
Time
Payment
COGS
Gross Margin Percentage
Gross Income
Rating

